{"type": "article", "id": 14777, "title": "组合沙发", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-11T07:11:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003270RIDdHKn9Jeb2sFC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组沙发成功合并了沙发、积木和床，可以卷成一个圆筒收起来，也可以展开成一个三角形的靠背和三片半圆的坐垫。对于年龄小一点的孩子，这就搭成了一个小型的游乐场，而父母们也可以直接当成坐垫。外表是羊毛布料，非常耐磨。现有灰色和蓝色可选，<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/roll-kids-cushion/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142224lHXgtL9iUp4oJ5Sh.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"599\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63723404\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142224CGYfRqg2ozEk47K5.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"605\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64361702\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142225dgEhcFBHM3atKnzs.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"554\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5893617\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}